3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper discusses the performance improvement of spatially coupled systems, which can be applied to social and information networks. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the potential function for characterizing the performance of spatially coupled systems, which is related to data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the performance improvement of belief-propagation algorithm, which is a common algorithm in machine learning.
